verbose_text: In addition, the expression levels of CAR, PXR and HNF4alpha genes in the cells grown on the MDS atelocollagen coat were significantly higher on day 7 compared with those in cells grown on conventional atelocollagen [6.6-fold (6.1 +/-0.8%), 1.5-fold (42.1 +/-5.7%), and 1.4-fold (57.0 +/-2.9%), respectively; XREF_FIG].
